description: THIS ONE CHECKS ALL THE BOXES! EAST SIDE CONDO QUALITY 1 BEDROOM/1 BATHROOM WITH ONE (1) OFF STREET PARKING SPOT AND COMMON ROOF DECK! CENTRALLY LOCATED IN SOUTH BOSTON JUST BLOCKS TO PUBLIC TRANSPORTATION, PARKS/BEACHES, SEAPORT DISTRICT, HIGHWAY ACCESS AND ALL OF SOUTHIE'S HOTTEST NEW SHOPS, BARS AND RESTAURANTS.
